              <b>
               event_i
              </b>
              will contain between 1 and 1,000 elements, inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <b>
               event_j
              </b>
              will contain the same number of elements as
              <b>
               event_i
              </b>
