                    Gold will be discovered in the cell (0, 0) today and in the cell (2, 2) tomorrow.
Note that you cannot move directly from (0, 0) to (2, 2), because both the difference in rows and the difference in columns is too great.
One optimal strategy is to work in the cell (0, 0) today and in the cell (1, 1) tomorrow.
Your profit today will be 6, tomorrow it will be 4, thus the total profit is 6+4 = 10.
